Privacy Policy for Luma

At Luma, accessible from https://discord.gg/49YNgs8dEq, one of our main priorities is the privacy of our visitors. This Privacy Policy document contains types of information that is collected and recorded by Luma and how we use it.

If you have additional questions or require more information about our Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact us.

This Privacy Policy applies only to our online activities and is valid for visitors to our website with regards to the information that they shared and/or collect in Luma. This policy is not applicable to any information collected offline or via channels other than this bot.

Consent

By using our bot, you hereby consent to our Privacy Policy and agree to its terms.

Information we collect

We dont collect any information of users, servers, channels or roles. So you cant contact us to delete datas, because we dont collect any kind of datas.
