Third Party Privacy Policies

Luma's Privacy Policy does not apply to other advertisers or bots. Thus, we are advising you to consult the respective Privacy Policies of these third-party ad servers for more detailed information. It may include their practices and instructions about how to opt-out of certain options.

Children's Information

Another part of our priority is adding protection for children while using the internet. We encourage parents and guardians to observe, participate in, and/or monitor and guide their online activity.

Luma does not knowingly collect any Personal Identifiable Information from children. If you think that your child provided this kind of information on our bot, we strongly encourage you to contact us immediately and we will do our best efforts to promptly remove such information from our records.
